trans-unit.source: Provides a listener that routes all tracing and debugging output to the [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Fornece um serviço de escuta que encaminha todos os rastreio e depuração de saída para o [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] infraestrutura.

trans-unit.source: The IisTraceListener class connects the tracing mechanism of [!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/add/includes/vstecasp-md.md)] to [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: A classe de IisTraceListener liga o mecanismo de rastreio de [!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/add/includes/vstecasp-md.md)] para [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: This listener class enables developers who create [!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/add/includes/vstecasp-md.md)] applications and who implement the <xref:System.Web.IHttpModule> and <xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler> interfaces to raise page-level, module-level, or handler-level events to the [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] infrastructure when tracing is enabled.
trans-unit.target: Esta classe de serviço de escuta permite aos programadores que criam [!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/add/includes/vstecasp-md.md)] e aplicações que implementa o <xref:System.Web.IHttpModule>e <xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler>interfaces para elevar o nível de página, ao nível do módulo ou ao nível do processador de eventos para o [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] infraestrutura quando o rastreio está ativada.</xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler> </xref:System.Web.IHttpModule>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > This listener class does not route [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] events to ASP.NET classes.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Esta classe de serviço de escuta não encaminhar [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] eventos para classes do ASP.NET.

trans-unit.source: This includes the <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> class and classes that implement the <xref:System.Web.IHttpModule> or <xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler> interface.
trans-unit.target: Isto inclui o <xref:System.Web.UI.Page>classe e classes que implementam o <xref:System.Web.IHttpModule>ou <xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler>interface.</xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler> </xref:System.Web.IHttpModule> </xref:System.Web.UI.Page>
